OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOften cloudy
OL,6,Fthis evening and overnight with
OL,7,Foccasional clear periods. Whilst a few
OL,8,Fshowers are possible, most places will
OL,9,Fremain dry. Turning chilly with a risk
OL,10,Fof a frost in the countryside, though
OL,11,Fthis probably less widespread than
OL,12,Flast night.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTuesday:FA cloudy start for some, but
OL,15,Fbecoming increasingly sunny with
OL,16,Fpatchy fair weather cloud. Feeling
OL,17,Fwarmer than on Monday though breezier
OL,18,Ftoo, with the easterly wind turning
OL,19,Fblustery at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
