OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:
OL,6,FStaying dry through the week with high
OL,7,Fpressure dominating, though breezy on
OL,8,FWednesday. Often sunny and turning
OL,9,Fwarmer by day. Chilly nights with
OL,10,Frural frosts possible as winds ease
OL,11,Fdown.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
